{"tid":1311341,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[陳煒fans入] 陳煒dry足7年拖手斷正 峇里陪醫生男友3日2夜","createTime":"2019-07-13T06:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T13:41:51.000Z","uid":49267,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f06b22a26e186dd1feb15ce33a4bb17b7d5a90b7","tid":1311341,"uid":49267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:37:34.000Z","msg":"現年45歲的陳煒曾經歷過婚姻失敗，單身7年，最近感情終於有着落！《蘋果》讀者李小姐日前透過「爆相爆片」分享，於上周六（6號）在峇里一個醫學研討會上，見到陳煒陪伴一位六呎高的猛男醫生到場，在酒店浪漫手牽手，好有初戀feel。<br />\n<br />\n當日陳煒打扮得好端莊，穿上一條長裙襯白色外套，心口掛住一個工作證件，全程坐在台上陪住醫生男友聽講座。李小姐透露這個醫學研討會在峇里一間五星級酒店的會議廳內舉行，由7月5日至7日，為期三天，當日下午12時許，見陳煒與醫生男友一同坐在台上，她說：「有幾位醫生輪流發言，同陳煒一齊嚟嗰位醫生都有演講，陳煒就用手機幫佢拍攝，好專注。」研討會大約一小時後結束，眾人在台上合照，陳煒都有份，她續說：「見佢哋手拖手行落台，之後啲人走得七七八八，佢哋又拖手上台再影相，仲有蹺手，好sweet。」<br />\n<br />\n從拍攝得來的影片可見，陳煒全程笑到四萬咁口，她先輕輕搭住對方膊頭，示意回頭一望。兩人傾了幾句，陳煒便熟練地伸手欲拖住醫生男友，但由於當時二人有少許距離，醫生男友便反過來捉住陳煒的手腕，兩人拉扯一會，最後合體，十字緊扣返回台上。李小姐透露翌日亦見到二人在酒店內出現，她說：「佢哋應該住同一間酒店，第二日嘅研討會都有參與。」<br />\n<br />\n根據研討會的網頁資料顯示，與陳煒同行的醫生名叫陳國強（Dr.Aldous Chan）。年約40歲的Aldous，據悉都是失婚人士，去年6月與黃智賢和另一位戴醫生合資在中環開設醫學美容中心，開張當日陳煒亦有盛裝到場，二人好可能就是在當日認識。而陳煒與黃智賢一向好老友，合作過好幾部劇集，黃智賢曾說過會幫陳煒物色好男人：「我幫佢留意緊嘅，但佢係冠軍級人馬，要有番咁上下先介紹得。」估唔到，黃智賢最後都能成功牽紅線。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否有新戀情？陳煒今日以短訊回覆傳媒：「了解中，多謝關心。」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465149208d9632bd7b8f1ed3f007adf3f9aa8ca3","tid":1311341,"uid":49267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DF1G32X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDF1G32X.jpg&h=65fccd5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aab0bdf2aac192b3b1a972d73526c1d608d1573c","tid":1311341,"uid":49267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTaHOuK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTaHOuK.jpg&h=f02ecd0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c88415c6548f9282a3ba9548a1a2b41a5b53b7b","tid":1311341,"uid":49267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocNfo3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocNfo3g.jpg&h=b0830b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QkD6gC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QkD6gC.jpg&h=f674e8f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f1cb73b6e681fc1695375eddeae403939704b9a","tid":1311341,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:42:20.000Z","msg":"四十路痴女"},{"pid":"6a06348377c1a5b189a0126c3a7358b3b49e6279","tid":1311341,"uid":119864,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:47:07.000Z","msg":"tvb又make noise，大家一齊負評<br />\n<br />\nps: 汁柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"335d19c588cf8c2757055683e66552a1192a9de2","tid":1311341,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"個下盤大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a731fafed6f0963b2bcd2ec72574306303a5396f","tid":1311341,"ui